comments: Rivers (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Winslow's (MIA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Harden's (HOU) path and the contact does not affect his ability to maintain his obtained position.
Richardson (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Capela's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
Harden (HOU) rests his hand against Wade's (MIA) side during his dribble but removes it as Wade (MIA) begins his upward shooting motion.
Capela (HOU) briefly grasps Adebayo's (MIA) right arm during rebounding, but does not affect his ability to back-tap the ball.
Paul (HOU) makes body contact with Richardson (MIA) after he returns to the floor and does not affect his ability to follow through naturally.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
MOB shows Richardson (MIA) attempts to defend around the pick and makes marginal contact with Paul (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
Rivers (HOU) swipes down and makes contact to Winslow's (MIA) wrist which affects his driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) enters the lane prior to the release of Winslow's (MIA) free throw attempt.
Capela (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Richardson's (MIA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Capela (HOU) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
LLS shows Richardson (MIA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Harden (HOU) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Green (HOU) makes contact with Waiters' (MIA) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt and does not affect his ability to follow through naturally.
Paul (HOU) grabs Wade's (MIA) left arm and initiates contact that affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
